title: Ayane-chan High Kick! (Ayane's High Kick)
synopsis: Ayane is a high school student focused on one thing, becoming a pro wrestler. A trainer tricks her into becoming a Kick Boxer, the sport she hates. She keeps with it though once she finds out.
